  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to validate the diagnostic correlation between the intraoperative
      microendoscopic images and the conventional histological analysis on biopsy and/or surgical
      specimens on patients with epidermoid carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
